# documentation-writer

Applies the Diátaxis framework to produce documentation in four modes:
*tutorials* (learning-oriented), *how-to guides* (goal-oriented), *reference*
(information-oriented), and *explanation* (understanding-oriented). Classifies
each writing task into the correct mode before drafting to keep docs
actionable, accurate, and easy to navigate.
